==========================================================
Download  songs by providing correct artist and song name
==========================================================

=============
Introduction:
=============
Download your favorite songs by just entering the artist and song title in this program. You can also give it a list of artists and the songs. Wait for sometime and you will have all those songs on your system :)

====================
Steps to run script
====================
1. Enter search terms for songs, preferably in the format <artist> - <song title> in songs.txt
2. Run script
3. Songs will be in the DownloadedSongs folder
4. Song name and corresponding YouTube URL is mentioned in songLinks.txt

=============
Dependencies
=============
1. python-2.7
2. youtube-dl
3. python packages used in the script